{"tid":45452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港豬冇得去旅行］大韓航空機師聖誕期間罷工　來往香港等受影響航班達84班","createTime":"2016-12-19T03:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T04:37:48.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c92c59cef6e7c4155380e2da3afee4ae1ed4538e","tid":45452,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"大韓航空機師工會因薪酬問題，決定將於聖誕期間罷工，預計受影響航班達84班，當中包括來往首爾至香港、日本等多條國際航線。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道，大韓航空機師工會去年起要求加薪，原擬要求加薪37%，後來減少至29%，惟公司堅持加薪幅度不能超過1.9%，令勞資雙方談判破裂。工會計劃本周四（22日）起罷工5日，估計有近200人參與。受影響的航班包括64條來往仁川、濟州島及金浦機場等地的國內航線，以及20條來往首爾至香港、日本及迪拜等多條國際航線。<br />\n<br />\n大韓航空公司表示，可維持大部分的航班服務，但22、24及25日來往香港及仁川、編號KE601和KE602的航班需要取消。當地國土交通部已與其他航空公司已召開緊急會議，設立應急控制委員會，必要時使用後備航班疏導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/194822/%e5%a4%a7%e9%9f%93%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e6%a9%9f%e5%b8%ab%e8%81%96%e8%aa%95%e6%9c%9f%e9%96%93%e7%bd%b7%e5%b7%a5%e3%80%80%e4%be%86%e5%be%80%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%ad%89%e5%8f%97%e5%bd%b1%e9%9f%bf%e8%88%aa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F194822%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%259f%2593%25e8%2588%25aa%25e7%25a9%25ba%25e6%25a9%259f%25e5%25b8%25ab%25e8%2581%2596%25e8%25aa%2595%25e6%259c%259f%25e9%2596%2593%25e7%25bd%25b7%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e3%2580%2580%25e4%25be%2586%25e5%25be%2580%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%25ad%2589%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e9%259f%25bf%25e8%2588%25aa%2F&d=iDWYYGGuCy9Wb6HPCWE4tHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=42461aeb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/194822/%e5%a4%a7%e9%9f%93%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e6%a9%9f%e5%b8%ab%e8%81%96%e8%aa%95%e6%9c%9f%e9%96%93%e7%bd%b7%e5%b7%a5%e3%80%80%e4%be%86%e5%be%80%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%ad%89%e5%8f%97%e5%bd%b1%e9%9f%bf%e8%88%aa/</a>"},{"pid":"d25682c171f64e2c6c1318d72a6f104ec11d41d5","tid":45452,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c70b1336ff7e85ed817261fa1eaf00f6ae6b185","tid":45452,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"英航都聖誕罷，等睇香港人話罷工做乜阻到佢"},{"pid":"51704a7cce0b7127349b63e8e340673b26e1cdbb","tid":45452,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:17:15.000Z","msg":"好想試下全香港罷工會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385930e21c8dc1c97b4c731ce0da2beec675cdbd","tid":45452,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"最多咪搭韓亞，再唔係搭大陸機。"},{"pid":"05d1889eb51f6fa625a731daa560ac79130ea95d","tid":45452,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英航都聖誕罷，等睇香港人話罷工做乜阻到佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n港豬思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}